<section id="writingtask1">
<p class="popuptext">You should spend about 40 minutes on this task.</p>

<p class="popuptext">Present a written argument or case to an educated reader with no specialist knowledge of the following topic:</p>

<p class="popuptext"><b>Ownership of mobile phones has risen dramatically in recent years despite the potentially harmful effects they may have on our health and on society. Governments should introduce measures to restrict ownership of mobile phones to those who need them for their work.</b></p>

<p class="popuptext"><b>To what extent do you agree or disagree with this statement?</b></p>

<p class="popuptext">You should wirte at least 250 words.</p>

<p class="popuptext">You should use your own ideas, knowledge and experience and support your arguments with examples and relevant evidence.</p>

